description: `TrStSaEUtranFreqRelProfile`: This table stores profiles defining UE mobility group configurations for E-UTRAN frequencies within specific cells and areas at a particular point in time.  Columns: `dateTime` (Timestamp of data collection), `Area_Name` (Geographic area), `CellId` (Unique cell identifier), `Id2` (Duplicate of CellId), `Id3` (Generic identifier, likely unused), `Id4` (Profile identifier), `vsDataType` (Data type identifier), `vsDataFormatVersion` (Version of data format), `TrStSaEUtranFreqRelProfile.userLabel` (User-defined label, currently empty), `TrStSaEUtranFreqRelProfile.reservedBy` (Reserved by field, currently empty), `TrStSaEUtranFreqRelProfile.ueConfGroupType` (Type of UE configuration group), `TrStSaEUtranFreqRelProfile.trStSaEUtranFreqRelProfileId` (Unique profile ID).
